Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,RightSignM - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz334.8\pos(392.199,239.556)}I'm at the Gotanno Station,\Nso I'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We-Wel-Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I'll leave the souvenirs\Nfrom the beach here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyways, how was it?\NThe beach... the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was fun. I got a lot of work done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A straw hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't it feel like summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And saying this might\Nhave the opposite effect, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One day, when you're able\Nto go outside again,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,let's go to the beach together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-S-Sagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't make any lewd misunderstandings.\NIt's a swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How is it? Does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell me what you think when we go for reals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go together someday.
