Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.45,CenterSignM - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\frz13.53\pos(30.516,416.889)}\N2017.9.9\NWritten by: Izumi Masamune\NIllustration: Eromanga
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It goes on sale tomorrow!\NI'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei! Eromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone by that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally, tomorrow is the release date\Nof our newest book!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A bookstore in Akiba is going to hold\Na "Izumi Masamune Faire" for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Want to go check it out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, this is what you meant\Nwhen you said "together".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a sibling date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now I have my third series.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's been three years since I debuted.\NIt felt long, yet short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nii-san, you started writing novels...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Back then, Mom had just passed away,\Nand the entire house was gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune... Are you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not lonely! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What should I do for my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you smile and live a joyous life,\Nthat's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're happy, we're happy.\NBecause we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Mom too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Ever since, I did all sorts of things,\Nthinking I had to find something I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everything was fun,\Nbut I couldn't get engrossed into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I found people\Nwriting stories on the internet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They seemed to have fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I thought, maybe this is it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You got hooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was super-duper fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a trigger for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, what were you\Ndoing back then, Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Refusing to go to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After Mom and Dad got divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't go to school for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}How did Hamanoumi do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By "for a while", you mean that afterwards,\Nyou got over it and started going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I don't know. You talk about sumo wresting\Na lot, but I don't know much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, there was a trigger for it.\NI went to grade school properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Eh? Why? Professional sumo is so amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go to middle school properly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}We're young enough to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what was your trigger?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, you're going to be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.23,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(347.15,121.333)\frz12.47}The Adventures of Masamune the Hero End of Episode 001
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.48,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz12.8\pos(452.266,324.445)}Episode 002 - NEW
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Do you pile up unpublished works?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you for the very first comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}What does it mean\Nto pile up unpublished works?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(644.833,9.333)}{\i1}When did you write this story?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Up to episode 10? All of it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yes! When I finish writing it,\NI upload them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}If you'd like, please tell me your thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Episode 011-015 NEW
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Hamanoumi advanced his rank\Nto juryo in professional sumo yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Episode 33 - Episode 35 NEW
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Episode 36 - Episode 38 NEW
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(802.95,90.222)}Episode 39 - Episode 40 NEW
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, it was the very first story\NI ever wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so it was worse than what I write now,\Nand pretty cringeworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"The Adventures\Nof Masamune the Hero", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were reading it, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-Forget about that story right now!\NGot that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am Masamune the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My special technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thunder God's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Annihilation Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.72,OnTop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10\frz340.5\pos(436.367,251.556)}Submission Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.87,CenterSignM - Copy (2),NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs9\pos(424,105.777)}The Adventures of Masamune the Hero The End
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.93,CenterSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(424,480,424,504.889,41,2919)}The Adventures of Masamune the Hero\NCongratulations\NCompletion of Story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a professional author!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, that's rather sudden.\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I came to a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was actually a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know, hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It just arrived, but I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going to be a professional author.\NYou need one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is super awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what got me hooked onto novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There was someone who said\Nthe first story I ever wrote was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was someone who drew illustrations\Nfor the characters I created.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It made me really happy,\Nand it was super-duper fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I aimed to become a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The only thing that linked us together\Nwas the novel website's forums and e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I think we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you watch the drama last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The other day, that main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you read my new piece?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not yet. I just woke up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You were still asleep?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you by chance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a NEET?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm a college student!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So you're an adult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! What about you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm 11!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. You're younger than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.35,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(429.3,336.444)}Sagiri, age 7, currently super in the middle of being a shut-in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to eat a Hamburg steak today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll see. I'll make some if ground meat\Nis cheap at the supermarket today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I drew another illustration for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously? Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, you know, can I attach it\Nto the story again and upload it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go ahead, but it's terrible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't matter at all. I really love it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, then I'll draw more for you.\NYou better be thankful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}More like, I'm basically the only one\Nwho reads your stories, anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Don't say that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Besides, the number of people\Nreading my stuff is growing bit by bit lately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Oh? Is it thanks to my illustrations?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}It's because my stories are interesting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.45,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10\frz103.4\pos(352.45,392)}Out of Order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Sagiri. Wouldn't school\Nbe a cooler place to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll never go. I rather be in a hot place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A picture like that\Ndoesn't make me want to lick her panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where did you learn stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, Sagiri, you've been\Nworking hard at drawing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why did you want to start\Nwriting stories?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- What's this so suddenly?\N- Just tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only have a dad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone gets worried\Nwhen I'm not enjoying life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, I thought I had to find something\NI liked doing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a dreary reason.\NIs stuff like that interesting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's super-duper interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you read what I write.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've gotten to like writing stories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.67,DefaultLow2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(287.967,224.444)}Adachi Ward Sakuranoshita \NElementary School's\N18th Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Congrats on graduating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I might keep playing\Nbadminton in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei, isn't this\Na few too many manuscripts to submit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the work of a genius, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm going to be a professional author.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Wow, such confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Maybe it will be just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please send these!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.88,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\frz333.3\pos(613.917,219.556)}Goodnight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.85,CenterSignM2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(287.967,284.444)\frz333.2}Do you like drawing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you like drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this so suddenly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(426.65,77.777)}I like it, because there's someone\Nwho gets happy with what I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.73,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\frz16.35\pos(468.166,407.555)}Because there's someone\Nwho gets happy with what I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:21.73,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\frz17.18\fs25\pos(295.033,303.555)}I like it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. Then, that's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to be a professional author!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this guy saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get so cocky. You suck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You said my stories were interesting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's interesting. But there's no way\Nyou'd become a professional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will! Because I'm a genius!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously, what is this guy saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just sent out a manuscript as a submission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm, I see. So you're serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should become a professional, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And draw characters for me again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This past year was really fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got my first review,\Nas well as my first illustration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I laughed a ton thanks to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do something\Neven more interesting tomorrow, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll become a professional author, and make\Ntons of people read super-interesting books,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and spend every day having fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, we should have fun together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's some boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't even know if that'll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will. I guarantee it as a genius.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't draw for your stories anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't send you e-mails either.\NYou should stop contacting me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to seriously start practicing\Nhow to draw from today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that I can make the dream\Nyou just gave me, come true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to make a book together,\Nand live every day laughing, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not a genius, so I don't\Nhave any more time to play around with kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't write novels\Nas a hobby anymore, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next time\Nwe contact each other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will be when we both become professionals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Teach me how to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Akihabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amazing! It's just like I've seen in anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want a tour of Akiba first!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.97,DefaultLef2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.716,350.223)}Onii-chan\NI love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.78,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz1.199\pos(613.917,15.556)}The World's Cutest Younger Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Eromanga", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've gotten used to it already,\NEromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know anyone by that name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's our book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, Sagiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I've been reunited with you,\Neverything's been really fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I laughed a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izumi-sensei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The first dream you've given me\Nhas come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's make this dream come true, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next time we contact each other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will be when we both become professionals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The World's Cutest Younger Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless to fret at this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone who's read my new book...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hope they had fun reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What happened to that confidence\Nyou used to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something\NI've been meaning to ask you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at this light-novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's going to be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The illustration is super-cute, too.\NIt looks like I can have high hopes for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Indeed, that illustration\Nhas quite a powerful soul within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, who knows about the contents?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The author of the book is someone I barely\Nknow about. A very minor-league author.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}- Now now, both of you, it is all fine.\N- Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it looks like\Nhe changed genres in this new series.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who knows if it will be interesting or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's better than the novel you just bought,\Nthe original story for that crappy anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pray the novel we created\Nwill be interesting for you, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}The original novels are interesting. Don't jump\Nto conclusions just by watching the anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can walk outside your room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.\NI'm overexerting myself, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been secretly practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. You've been putting in effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ugh, because you said something you didn't\Nneed to, I forgot about the main point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nii-san. Congratulations\Non the release of the new novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm home, Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei's illustrations\Nare really the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anyone by that—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, see ya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! See ya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My regards for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The pleasure is mine!
